142â†’Anthropic has not just come up with the protocol, they've also created [a great ecosystem around it](https://github.com/modelcontextprotocol): Various SDKs, reference servers and a visual testing tool: [The MCP Inspector](https://github.com/modelcontextprotocol/inspector).
143â†’
144â†’Let's modify our serve target to use the Inspector, letting us explore our newly created server. First, delete the existing `serve` target in `apps/mcp-server/package.json` , as it doesn't really apply to our use case. Replace it with this
